info.author: Matt Chisholm
info.description: PoParser is a Python library for parsing and programmatically manipulating GNU Gettext .po files. It can read and write .po files, and can easily be used to write scripts to diff, merge, batch modify, and restructure .po files.
info.name: PoParser
info.summary: parse and programmatically manipulate GNU Gettext .po files
